<p>Piece I</p>

<p>
<lb n="1"/><hi rend="grantha">svastiśrī</hi> tirumaṭantai
<lb n="2" break="no"/>laiyāka pārmuḻutuṅ kayalāṇai
<lb n="3" break="no"/>ṇṭu pattāvatu <hi rend="grantha">śrī</hi> pāṇṭi nāṭ
<lb n="4" break="no"/>ṟkkum Ivvicainta peru
</p>

<p>Piece II</p>

<p>
<lb n="1" break="no"/>vairellām vantiṟaiñca <gap reason="lost" quantity="5" unit="character"/> va <gap reason="lost" quantity="5" unit="character"/> makaḷ tiruppuyatti <gap reason="lost" quantity="5" unit="character"/> yāruk <gap reason="lost" quantity="2" unit="character"/> 
<lb n="2" break="no"/>caṭaiyapa<hi rend="grantha">nma</hi>rāṉa tiripuvaṉac cakkaravattikaḷ <hi rend="grantha">śrī</hi> vikrama pāṇṭiya tevaṟku yāṇṭu
<lb n="3" break="no"/>vallanāṭāṉa <hi rend="grantha">ja</hi>yaṅkoṇṭa pāṇṭiyapura <gap reason="lost" quantity="5" unit="character"/> 
<lb n="4"/>Āṭu Ēḻu Ivāṭu Ēḻukaik koṇṭu nittal nimantam <num value="200">2 <g type="numeral">100</g></num>kku ney cantirātittaval
<lb n="5" break="no"/>ṭāṉa <hi rend="grantha">ja</hi>yaṅkoṇṭa pāṇṭiyapurattu <hi rend="grantha">śrī</hi> kulacekara tevarkku yāṇṭu vallanāṭṭu <gap reason="lost" quantity="5" unit="character"/> <hi rend="grantha">śrī</hi> kocca
<lb n="6" break="no"/>ru <gap reason="lost" quantity="2" unit="character"/> ku celuttuveṉāka Ikkācu kaikkoṇṭeṉ paḷḷa <gap reason="lost" quantity="10" unit="character"/> celuttāta piṉpu kaṭavūr Appa <gap reason="lost" quantity="5" unit="character"/> tiruva <gap reason="lost" quantity="1" unit="character"/> rāya 
<lb n="7" break="no"/>paṭiyāṉ pakkal Ikkoyil tiruvaṭipiṭikkum tirukkaṇṇa <gap reason="lost" quantity="10" unit="character"/> 
</p>

<p>Piece III</p>

<p>
<lb n="1"/><hi rend="grantha">svastiśrī</hi> tirumaka
<lb n="2" break="no"/><ce>damaged</ce>
<lb n="3"/> <gap reason="lost" quantity="10" unit="character"/> vaṟa
<lb n="4" break="no"/><ce>damaged</ce>
<lb n="5"/>tāviḷakku cantira
<lb n="6" break="no"/>kaikkoṇṭu
</p>

<p>Piece IV</p>

<p>
<lb n="1" break="no"/>mum perumai Eyta Eṇṭicaiyuṅ kuṭai niḻaṟṟa maṉ
<lb n="2" break="no"/>koccaṭaiyapaṉmarāṉa <hi rend="grantha">tri</hi>puvanac cakkaravattikaḷ <hi rend="grantha">śrī</hi> vikkirama pāṇṭi
<lb n="3-4" break="no"/><ce>damaged</ce>
<lb n="5"/> <gap reason="lost" quantity="10" unit="character"/> taṅkaḷukku <gap reason="lost" quantity="10" unit="character"/> Ivvūrpura
</p>

<p>Piece V</p>

<p>
<lb n="1" break="no"/>ṉum piyarāl
<lb n="2" break="no"/>eḻuttiṭṭa Uḷ
<lb n="3" break="no"/>puḷikkum <gap reason="lost" quantity="2" unit="character"/> va
</p>

<p>Piece VI</p>

<p>
<lb n="1" break="no"/>āḷvārkku tiru
<lb n="2" break="no"/>kku vaṭakkum I
<lb n="3" break="no"/>nilam Irumāva
<lb n="4" break="no"/>ce veliyum
<lb n="5" break="no"/>ppatāka niroṭu vā
